sources.title: Sample People | FULL MOVIE | Ensemble Drama
sources.description:
In this thriller, four groups of Australians try to make their way out of Sydney over the course of a weekend. Starring Ben Mendelsohn ("Rogue One").

#2000s #freemoviesonline #thriller #benmendelsohn #australia #ozzy #actionmovies #horrorstories #sydney #sydneyaustralia #ensemble #comedy #2000smovies

metadata.Plot: This edgy Australian film stars an ensemble cast headed up by pop superstar Kylie Minogue, David Field, and Simon Lyndon. Various characters interact under strange circumstances, calling to mind movies such as GO and PULP FICTION.
metadata.Writer: Clinton Smith, Peter Buckmaster, Anthony O'Connor
metadata.Actors: Kylie Minogue, Ben Mendelsohn, Simon Lyndon
